# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Got Soap? — repo hygiene. The design sources in this directory
# reach ~1.7 GB (.abr brush packs). NOTHING large gets committed.
# Web-ready derivatives live under site/ and are committed there.
# See PRD §6.5 + CLAUDE.md "Asset warnings".
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
/zips/
/test/
/.mars/
/.meridian/
.claude/settings.local.json

/.agents/agents/
